{
  "theme_archetype": "Archetype 4 (Swiss & High-Contrast) infused with Berlin Raw Urban & Dark Mode Luxury",
  "design_rationale": "A stark, dark-mode-first approach reflecting Berlin's nightlife and raw urban edge, contrasting with a rich, vibrant crimson (a distinctive evolution of Airbnb red). We avoid standard dashboard templates by utilizing bold, high-contrast typography and generous padding.",
